/*
  Localizable.strings (en-GB)
  WoofWalk iOS

  UK English source-of-truth strings. Keys mirror the Android
  `app/src/main/res/values/strings.xml` naming convention so a
  future translation pipeline can drop in language packs across
  both platforms with a single dictionary.

  Phase 1 (this file) covers:
    - Common UI / actions / errors / loading / empty-state shells
    - Tabs + top-level navigation labels
    - Auth (login, signup, forgot-password)
    - Walk lifecycle + completion recap
    - Booking flow shell
    - Notifications, Settings, Profile, Friends list

  Future phases extend per-screen sections in-place; do NOT
  rename existing keys — they're load-bearing for both iOS
  callers (`String(localized: "key")`) and the cross-platform
  translation dictionary mapping back to Android string IDs.
*/

